General.Description: 1414 Degrees Limited offers thermal energy storage systems for networks and industries in Australia. It provides heat and electricity from renewable energy sources. The company was formerly known as Latent Heat Storage Pty Ltd. 1414 Degrees Limited was incorporated in 2009 and is based in Melrose Park, Australia.
